{
  "easy": {
    "title": "Build a Product Listing Page with 6 Cards",
    "description": "Create a single product listing page showing 6 product cards in a grid layout. Each card must include: product image, product name, price, rating (stars), and an Add to Cart button. Use semantic HTML5 elements (<article> for each card). Include a simple header with a search bar and a footer.",
    "starterCode": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Shop - Our Products</title>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Our Shop</h1>\n        <form action=\"search.html\" method=\"GET\">\n            <input type=\"search\" name=\"q\" placeholder=\"Search products...\">\n        </form>\n    </header>\n    <main>\n        <h2>Featured Products</h2>\n        <div class=\"product-grid\">\n            <!-- Add 6 product cards here -->\n        </div>\n    </main>\n</body>\n</html>",
    "solution": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"Browse our collection of featured products with ratings and prices.\">\n    <title>Shop - Our Products</title>\n    <style>\n        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; }\n        header { background: #2c3e50; color: white; padding: 1rem 2rem; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }\n        header input { padding: 0.5rem; border-radius: 5px; border: none; width: 250px; }\n        .product-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; padding: 2rem; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }\n        .product-card { background: white; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); transition: transform 0.2s; }\n        .product-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); }\n        .product-image { height: 200px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 4em; }\n        .product-info { padding: 1rem; }\n        .product-info h3 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #2c3e50; }\n        .price { font-size: 1.3em; font-weight: bold; color: #e74c3c; margin: 0.5rem 0; }\n        .rating { color: #f39c12; margin: 0.3rem 0; }\n        .add-to-cart { background: #3498db; color: white; border: none; padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; width: 100%; font-size: 1em; }\n        .add-to-cart:hover { background: #2980b9; }\n        footer { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; background: #2c3e50; color: white; margin-top: 2rem; }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Our Shop</h1>\n        <form action=\"search.html\" method=\"GET\"><input type=\"search\" name=\"q\" placeholder=\"Search products...\"></form>\n    </header>\n    <main>\n        <h2 style=\"text-align:center;padding:1rem;\">Featured Products</h2>\n        <div class=\"product-grid\">\n            <article class=\"product-card\">\n                <div class=\"product-image\" style=\"background:#3498db;\">&#128187;</div>\n                <div class=\"product-info\">\n                    <h3>Laptop Pro</h3>\n                    <div class=\"rating\">★★★★☆</div>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$1,299.99</p>\n                    <button class=\"add-to-cart\">Add to Cart</button>\n                </div>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"product-card\">\n                <div class=\"product-image\" style=\"background:#e74c3c;\">&#128241;</div>\n                <div class=\"product-info\">\n                    <h3>SmartPhone X</h3>\n                    <div class=\"rating\">★★★★★</div>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$899.99</p>\n                    <button class=\"add-to-cart\">Add to Cart</button>\n                </div>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"product-card\">\n                <div class=\"product-image\" style=\"background:#2ecc71;\">&#127911;</div>\n                <div class=\"product-info\">\n                    <h3>Wireless Headphones</h3>\n                    <div class=\"rating\">★★★☆☆</div>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$149.99</p>\n                    <button class=\"add-to-cart\">Add to Cart</button>\n                </div>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"product-card\">\n                <div class=\"product-image\" style=\"background:#f39c12;\">&#128188;</div>\n                <div class=\"product-info\">\n                    <h3>Smart Watch</h3>\n                    <div class=\"rating\">★★★★☆</div>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$249.99</p>\n                    <button class=\"add-to-cart\">Add to Cart</button>\n                </div>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"product-card\">\n                <div class=\"product-image\" style=\"background:#9b59b6;\">&#128187;</div>\n                <div class=\"product-info\">\n                    <h3>Tablet Air</h3>\n                    <div class=\"rating\">★★★★☆</div>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$449.99</p>\n                    <button class=\"add-to-cart\">Add to Cart</button>\n                </div>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"product-card\">\n                <div class=\"product-image\" style=\"background:#1abc9c;\">&#128266;</div>\n                <div class=\"product-info\">\n                    <h3>Bluetooth Speaker</h3>\n                    <div class=\"rating\">★★★☆☆</div>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$79.99</p>\n                    <button class=\"add-to-cart\">Add to Cart</button>\n                </div>\n            </article>\n        </div>\n    </main>\n    <footer><p>&copy; 2026 Our Shop. All rights reserved.</p></footer>\n</body>\n</html>"
  },
  "medium": {
    "title": "Build a Product Detail + Cart + Checkout Flow",
    "description": "Create a 3-page e-commerce flow: product.html (product detail page with image gallery, description, specs, reviews, and Add to Cart), cart.html (shopping cart table with quantity inputs, remove button, coupon code field, and totals), and checkout.html (checkout form with shipping info, payment fields, order summary, and form validation). All pages must share consistent header and footer.",
    "starterCode": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Product Detail</title>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header><!-- Shared header --></header>\n    <main>\n        <nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\"><ol><li><a href=\"index.html\">Home</a></li><li><a href=\"category.html\">Category</a></li><li aria-current=\"page\">Product</li></ol></nav>\n        <!-- Product detail content -->\n    </main>\n    <footer><!-- Shared footer --></footer>\n</body>\n</html>",
    "solution": "Create 3 HTML files with consistent header/footer. Product.html: full product detail with schema.org product structured data. Cart.html: table-based cart with quantity controls and summary. Checkout.html: form with fieldset groups, validation attributes, and proper labeling."
  },
  "hard": {
    "title": "Build a Complete E-Commerce Store with 8+ Pages",
    "description": "Create a complete e-commerce store with: Home (hero, featured products, categories), Category (sidebar filters, product grid with pagination), Product Detail (image gallery, specs, reviews, related products), Cart (full cart management), Checkout (multi-section form), Account (login/register forms, order history), Search Results (with filter/sort), and Confirmation (order summary). Include: Schema.org structured data on product pages, breadcrumb navigation on all pages, responsive design, autocomplete on checkout forms, and a 404 page.",
    "starterCode": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>ShopName - Home</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"assets/css/style.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <a href=\"index.html\" class=\"logo\">ShopName</a>\n        <nav>\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"index.html\">Home</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"category.html\">Shop</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"cart.html\">Cart (0)</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"account.html\">Account</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n    <main><!-- Content varies per page --></main>\n    <footer><!-- Shared footer with 4 columns --></footer>\n</body>\n</html>",
    "solution": "Build 8+ HTML files. Home: hero banner + featured grid + category links. Category: sidebar filters + product grid + pagination. Product: structured data + gallery + specs. Cart: table + summary + coupon. Checkout: multi-section form with validation. Account: login/register forms + order history table. Search: filters + grid. Confirmation: order details. All share consistent layout via one CSS file."
  }
